Maryse Guy Mitsouko https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maryse_Guy_Mitsouko 0 Maryse Guy Mitsouko (born Maryse Guy; 1943 – March 1995) was a Eurasian striptease artist and actress. She was mostly billed as Mitsouko. She made her debut in Douce Violence in 1962. Mitsouko is most known for playing a minor Bond girl Madame La Porte in Thunderball (where her voice was dubbed by Catherine Clemence) as well as appearing in several other Eurospy films such as Agent 077 - Mission Bloody Mary.
